{"data":[{"date":"00:34 21/07","title":"Liverpool ch\u1ea3nh, n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/liverpool-chanh-noi-khong-voi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jurgen Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lyon m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 hai.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p, Nabil Fekir c\u0169ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Jean Michael Aulas \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u1ed1i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Liverpool tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool kh\u00f4ng mua Fekir d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lyon ch\u00e0o m\u1eddi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool kh\u00f4ng mua Fekir d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lyon ch\u00e0o m\u1eddi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/liverpool-chanh-noi-khong-voi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool kh\u00f4ng mua Fekir d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lyon ch\u00e0o m\u1eddi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng, ch\u00ednh Lyon c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1ea1t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o, ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean m\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t chuy\u1ec7n gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf \u1edf Anfield.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0ng cho Lyon, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau khi Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Xherdan Shaqiri \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf, kh\u1ecfa l\u1eadp th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 v\u1ed3 h\u1ee5t n\u00e0y. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf v\u00f9ng Merseyside \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea1o chi \u0111\u1ebfn x\u1ea5p x\u1ec9 175 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho 4 t\u00e2n binh, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Alisson Becker, v\u1eady n\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n d\u01b0 d\u1ea3 ng\u00e2n qu\u1ef9 cho th\u00eam m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n n\u00e0o n\u1eefa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Jurgen Klopp c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Liverpool s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Fekir n\u1eefa. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi r\u1ed3i, v\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ai n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a CLB.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1467","checkdouble":"191696"},{"date":"01:38 21/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00e2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1i \u1edf Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/Sokratis-Papastathopoulos-991489.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sokratis Papastathopoulos h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd h\u1ebft l\u00f2ng d\u00ecu d\u1eaft v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e0n em \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Konstantinos Mavropanos v\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u1edf Arsenal.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng n\u1eeda n\u0103m m\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Hy L\u1ea1p \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB. Th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Konstantinos Mavropanos b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Emirates v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i s\u00e1u th\u00e1ng sau, Sokratis Papastathopoulos c\u0169ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17,6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Dortmund.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis v\u00e0 Mavropanos c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1ee3 l\u1eabn nhau h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis v\u00e0 Mavropanos c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1ee3 l\u1eabn nhau h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/Sokratis-Papastathopoulos-991489.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis v\u00e0 Mavropanos c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn sau nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e0n anh d\u1ea1n d\u00e0y kinh nghi\u1ec7m, Sokratis c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t ra d\u00e1ng khi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd d\u00ecu d\u1eaft, ch\u1ec9 b\u1ea3o t\u1eadn t\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0n em \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 30 tu\u1ed5i:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Arsenal tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c nhau. V\u00ed d\u1ee5 v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00ec ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y, ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh l\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Dino r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang ta gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Arsenal n\u00ean r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 xem c\u1eadu \u1ea5y thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cN\u1eeda m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Dino g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb m\u1edbi ch\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbt ch\u00e2n r\u00e1o gia nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi cao. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ee1 ng\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec c\u00f3 t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ed3i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111i\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1m v\u00e0 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1466","checkdouble":"191697"},{"date":"04:18 21/07","title":"Neymar tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u00dd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/neymar-tin-ronaldo-se-toa-sang-tren-dat-y.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u00dd, CLB Juventus \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb CLB Chelsea.</h2><h2>Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Chelsea cho trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Chelsea cho trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/13/Juventus-tu-choi-de-nghi-cua-Chelsea-cho-trung-ve-Mattia-Caldara-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara c\u1ee7a Chelsea</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Trong m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, CLB Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara t\u1edbi Juve, tuy nhi\u00ean ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, \u2018L\u00e3o b\u00e0\u2019 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Caldara t\u1eeb Chelsea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>Theo Sky Sport Italia th\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Juve kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch v\u1edbi Caldara v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Juve c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro (27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) cho trung v\u1ec7 Caldara. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Dortmund c\u0169ng g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 35 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng b\u1ecb nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>Trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Juve cho Atalanta m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Anh ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 34 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn L\u00e3o b\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1465","checkdouble":"191698"},{"date":"05:16 21/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 21/7: \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sao PSG li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2015/2/2/Blanc-mo-duong-cho-sao-tre-PSG-den-MU-hinh-anh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sao PSG li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi M.U, Liverpool t\u1eeb b\u1ecf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir, PSG c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Neymar,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 21/7.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sao PSG li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi M.U<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB Man United \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Marquinhos c\u1ee7a PSG. T\u1edd Paris United ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 si\u00eau c\u00f2 Giuliano Bertolucci, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Marquinhos, \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi Man United \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Marquinhos c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi Man United. \u00d4ng Bertolucci \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng d\u00e0nh cho anh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 217 \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sao PSG li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 217 \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sao PSG li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-217-Dai-dien-sao-PSG-lien-he-voi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Marquinhos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 BL\u0110 M.U \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Chelsea sang \u00dd t\u1ef1 tay chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italy, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Chelsea Abramovich v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean gia chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng&nbsp;Fali Ramadani \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Milan \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o&nbsp;Gonzalo Higuain v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Daniele Rugani v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd&nbsp;Corriere dello Sport&nbsp;kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Juventus&nbsp;Fabio Paratici \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u00e1i \u0111o\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00f4m 18/7. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n chi 115,9 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y. 69,7 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la cho Higuain v\u00e0 46,2 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la cho Rugani.</p>\r\n<h2>Lamela k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Tottenham</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Erik Lamela l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd m\u1ed9t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u1eadu l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n, giao k\u00e8o n\u00e0y s\u1ebd h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2022. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Heung-min Son c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 5 n\u0103m trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Tottenham Hotspur.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>T\u00e2n binh Chelsea t\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n h\u00f4m 19/7, t\u00e2n binh Jorginho c\u1ee7a Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n so v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jorginho n\u00f3i: ''C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 hy v\u1ecdng n\u00f3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n n\u00f3&rdquo;. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italy g\u1ed1c Brazil \u0111\u00e1p: ''T\u00f4i th\u00edch ch\u01a1i ngay ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i''.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>PSG c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Neymar<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Qatar cho bi\u1ebft, c\u00e1c \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a PSG s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Kylian Mbappe. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Neymar, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o HLV Thomas Tuchel. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t thanh ti\u1ebfng T\u00e2y Ban Nha&nbsp;El Transistor&nbsp;c\u1ee7a k\u00eanh&nbsp;Onda Cero.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edd AS c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Tuchel kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Neymar b\u1eb1ng Mbappe. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf th\u00edch h\u1ee3p, nh\u01b0&nbsp;Paulo Dybala ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Liverpool r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Nabil Fekir<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Liverpool Echo cho hay, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Nabil Fekir trong m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. T\u1edd b\u00e1o tr\u00ean c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00eam Alisson c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 bom t\u1ea5n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a The Kop \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi bao g\u1ed3m: Shaqiri, Fabinho, Naby Keita v\u00e0 Alissson. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Danny Ward cho Leicester v\u00e0 cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n Daniel Sturbridge. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin sang Real, Hazard v\u1eabn qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi cho Chelsea<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Hazard \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid sau th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 tung ra b\u1ed9 \u1ea3nh qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o m\u1eabu \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard. Nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V The Blues l\u1ea1i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng sang Real Madrid nh\u01b0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>HLV Enrique \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f9ng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e1o ch\u00ed TBN cho bi\u1ebft t\u00e2n HLV Luis Enrique mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec9nh cao sau ba th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 EURO v\u00e0 World Cup g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 l\u00e0m h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00e0 chinh ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfc Cup ti\u1ebfp theo - EURO 2020 trong hai n\u0103m n\u1eefa'', Enrique chia s\u1ebb trong l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft h\u00f4m 19/7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Zidane kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda l\u00e0m HLV tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2020<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p Noel Le Graet \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho HLV \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m Didier Deschamps sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: &quot;Ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c thay Didier Deschamps. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e8 2020. Ngay c\u1ea3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 k\u00e9m s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Deschamps s\u1ebd t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&quot;.<br>\r\nXEM TH\u00caM:&nbsp;<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-207-184-191687.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 20/7: B\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a HLV Arsene Wenger</span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1464","checkdouble":"191700"},{"date":"05:35 21/07","title":"Real mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201cs\u00e1t th\u1ee7\u201d Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo t\u1edd Marca, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, Mauro Icardi \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</h2><h2>Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Icardi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Icardi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/17/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-chieu-mo-Icardi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Real Madrid \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, Mauro Icardi</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u00e0 Mauro Icardi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft t\u00e2n binh Alvaro Odriozola, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn\u00a0cho Real v\u00e0 Mauro Icardi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia TBN.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/19, Icardi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 29 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 36 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cho Inter. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Icardi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111ang c\u1ea7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, BL\u0110 Real \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Icardi. Real c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1ee9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch PSG ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u1edbi Barca, khi m\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Mauro Icardi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 110 tri\u1ec7u euro.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u00dd \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9 tin CLB Inter \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Icardi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 2023 v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 7,5 \u0111\u1ebfn 8 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a, cao h\u01a1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 5,5 tri\u1ec7u euro \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch Inter chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i Champions League.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2007-180-191661.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2007.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2007-180-191661.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 20/07</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 20/07.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/neymar-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-187-191656.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/neymar-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/neymar-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-187-191656.html\">Neymar ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi PSG d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb CLB Real Madrid.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1463","checkdouble":"191701"},{"date":"05:48 21/07","title":"Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/15/juventus-tu-choi-phu-phang-de-nghi-chuyen-nhuong-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u00dd, CLB Juventus \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb CLB Chelsea.</h2><h2>Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Chelsea cho trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Chelsea cho trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/13/Juventus-tu-choi-de-nghi-cua-Chelsea-cho-trung-ve-Mattia-Caldara-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara c\u1ee7a Chelsea</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Trong m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, CLB Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara t\u1edbi Juve, tuy nhi\u00ean ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, \u2018L\u00e3o b\u00e0\u2019 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Caldara t\u1eeb Chelsea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>Theo Sky Sport Italia th\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Juve kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch v\u1edbi Caldara v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Juve c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro (27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) cho trung v\u1ec7 Caldara. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Dortmund c\u0169ng g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 35 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng b\u1ecb nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>Trung v\u1ec7 Mattia Caldara \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Juve cho Atalanta m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Anh ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 34 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn L\u00e3o b\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1462","checkdouble":"191702"},{"date":"06:10 21/07","title":"\u0110\u00e3 xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/5/da-xong-tuong-lai-tien-dao-son-heungmin.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CLB Tottenham m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min.</h2><h2>Tottenham gia h\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung-Min\" title=\"Son Heung-Min\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-Min ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Tottenham t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2023</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-min l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n b\u00ean ph\u00eda Tottenham \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Anh ghi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 27 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 \u0103n \u00fd khi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ea1nh Dele Alli v\u00e0 Christian Eriksen \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i ngay ph\u00eda sau trung phong Harry Kane.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Son Heung-Min l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap&nbsp;anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn bao g\u1ed3m c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 M.U, Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool. Tuy nhi\u00ean Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00e2n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng x\u1ea5u nh\u1ea5t x\u1ea3y ra.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-minM\u01a1\u0301i \u0111\u00e2y, trang chu\u0309 Tottenham th\u00f4ng ba\u0301o \u0111\u00f4\u0323i bo\u0301ng \u0111a\u0303 gi\u01b0\u0303 ch\u00e2n tha\u0300nh c\u00f4ng Son Heung-min. Ng\u00f4i sao cu\u0309a \u0110T Ha\u0300n Qu\u00f4\u0301c se\u0303 g\u0103\u0301n bo\u0301 v\u01a1\u0301i Spurs \u0111\u00ea\u0301n n\u0103m 2023. \u0110\u00e2y la\u0300 quy\u00ea\u0301t \u0111i\u0323nh quan tro\u0323ng trong b\u00f4\u0301i ca\u0309nh chu\u0309 ti\u0323ch Daniel Levy \u0111ang co\u0301 nhi\u00ea\u0300u tham vo\u0323ng tr\u01b0\u01a1\u0301c mu\u0300a gia\u0309i m\u01a1\u0301i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c Harry Kane v\u00e0 Lamela \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cho th\u1ea5y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Spurs tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ea1ng 3 chung cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi 77 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1461","checkdouble":"191703"},{"date":"06:31 21/07","title":"G\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n 3, Barca quy\u1ebft mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, CLB Barcelona v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 ba \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Willian t\u1eeb Chelsea.</h2><h2>Barca quy\u1ebft mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e2u, ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Sky Sports&nbsp;kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh CLB Barca \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, Willian l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh. \u1ede l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 b\u1edfi Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian\" title=\"Willian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/5/Sao-khung-Chelsea-bao-tin-cuc-vui-cho-MU-va-Barca-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB Barcelona g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 h\u1ecfi mua Willian</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u0129 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, Willian \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 M.U v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 Chelsea t\u1ecf ra h\u1edd h\u1eefng v\u1edbi Barca.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Blaugrana \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Willian. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 La Liga \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3, tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi ph\u00eda The Blues kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 Willian \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho M.U, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi HLV Sarri v\u1ec1 Chelsea, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Willian c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Brazil \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin c\u01b0\u0323u c\u00e2\u0300u thu\u0309 Shaktar Donetsk se\u0303 r\u01a1\u0300i Chelsea ngay trong mu\u0300a He\u0300 n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Willian v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n trong 2 n\u0103m n\u1eefa, do \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp sang tu\u1ed5i 30 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/da-xong-tuong-lai-tien-dao-son-heungmin-172-191703.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/5/da-xong-tuong-lai-tien-dao-son-heungmin.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/da-xong-tuong-lai-tien-dao-son-heungmin-172-191703.html\">\u0110\u00e3 xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min</span><br>\r\nCLB Tottenham m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Son Heung-min.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-tu-choi-phu-phang-de-nghi-chuyen-nhuong-cua-chelsea-172-191702.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/15/juventus-tu-choi-phu-phang-de-nghi-chuyen-nhuong-cua-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-tu-choi-phu-phang-de-nghi-chuyen-nhuong-cua-chelsea-172-191702.html\">Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi \u00dd, CLB Juventus \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb CLB Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1460","checkdouble":"191704"},{"date":"06:42 21/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (21/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2172018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 21/7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam/r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 21-7-2018 v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 21-7-2018 v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00