1b0\u01a1ng vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 21/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/21/nhan-dinh-binh-duong-vs-da-nang-17h00-ngay-217-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 21/7 (V\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 217 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 17h00 ng\u00e0y 217 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/binh-duong-vs-da-nang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span>B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: 3-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu\u00a0 v\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. 4 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf V-League, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0o (thua 2), trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec v\u1eady, \u1edf m\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 chi\u1ec1u nay, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 9 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf V-League 2018 (thua 3). Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd m\u1ed9t chi ti\u1ebft quan tr\u1ecdng: \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, trong 9 tr\u1eadn xa nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 qua, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 thua t\u1edbi 7. S\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua m\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch l\u00e0 20.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n c\u00f2n d\u00ednh t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 sau tr\u1eadn thua TP\u00a0H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh 2-4. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 4 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh V\u0103n H\u01b0ng. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, n\u01a1i m\u00e0 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi thua duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng c\u00f3 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 10 tr\u00ean BXH, k\u00e9m 2 b\u1eadc so v\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00edch th\u1ecb l\u00e0 \u201cvua h\u00f2a\u201d c\u1ee7a V-League 2018 (11/19 tr\u1eadn). M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 G\u00f2 \u0110\u1eadu, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, trong 9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 thua 2. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 18 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 4 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf V-League (th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n- 5/6 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n- B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1/7 cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf V-League (th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 2, thua 4).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: T\u1ea5n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u2013 Trung T\u00edn, H\u1ed3 T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, Thanh Th\u1ea3o, Rabo, L\u00ea T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, D\u0169 \u0110\u1ea1t, Anh T\u00e0i, Ti\u1ebfn Linh, S\u1ef9 Gi\u00e1p, Onyelonu.<br>\r\n+ \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng: Thanh B\u00ecnh \u2013 V\u0103n Long, Ewonde, Vi\u1ec7t Anh, Anh Quang, Thanh H\u1ea3i, Ng\u1ecdc Th\u1eafng, Tr\u1ecdng H\u00f3a, Ti\u1ebfn D\u1ee5ng, Kouassi, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1458","checkdouble":"191706"},{"date":"15:01 20/07","title":"C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Mua Eden Hazard th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Le10 Sport \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Los Blancos \u0111ang ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d t\u1eeb Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEden Hazard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid theo \u0111u\u1ed5i trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, song ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Mua Eden Hazard th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Mua Eden Hazard th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Real-Mua-Eden-Hazard-thanh-cong-voi-gia-sieu-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Hazard \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111ang b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real, NHM \u0111ang g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p bu\u1ed9c BL\u0110 Los Blancos ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Khi m\u00e0 Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe b\u1ecb PSG h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao th\u00ec Hazard tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd chi \u0111\u1eadm mua ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, Hazard kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cM\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real\u201d. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Chelsea: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea 6 n\u0103m, t\u00f4i \u0111ang suy ngh\u0129 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac vi\u1ec7c ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real mua Hazard th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Mua Eden Hazard th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Le10 Sport \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Los Blancos \u0111ang ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d t\u1eeb Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real muon mua bang duoc Eden Hazard\" title=\"Real mu\u1ed1n mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Eden Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, Real \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt g\u1eb7p ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 7 tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho anh m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHazard \u0111\u00e3 \u01b0ng v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Real, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0a ra khi\u1ebfn Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Th\u1ef1c ra, The Blues v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Hazard \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng thu v\u1ec1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng thay th\u1ebf cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-115-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-hazard-172-191418.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea chi 115 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Martial</span>, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Leon Bailey c\u1ee7a CLB Bayer Leverkusen c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Blues nh\u1eafm thay Hazard.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1457","checkdouble":"191665"},{"date":"14:49 20/07","title":"Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/man-city-len-ke-hoach-chia-tay-sterling.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man City, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Raheem Sterling \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</h2><h2>Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay Sterling</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay Sterling h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay Sterling h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Man-City-len-ke-hoach-chia-tay-Sterling-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Raheem Sterling \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn Man City t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn khi tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Raheem Sterling gia nh\u1eadp CLB Man City t\u1eeb Liverpool v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh, k\u00e8m th\u00eam 5 tri\u1ec7u ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 \u1edf x\u1ee9 s\u1edf S\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2020. Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y Sterling v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Man xanh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ed9t m\u1ef1c h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau khi World Cup 2018 k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1edf d\u0129 Sterling kh\u00f4ng v\u1ed9i v\u00e3 gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Man xanh b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n anh \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n gia h\u1ea1n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u1edbi BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Sterling \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 170,000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Daily Mirror,\u00a0tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Sterling, BL\u0110 Man City \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra gi\u1eadn d\u1eef v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ngay trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Pep c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn khi chia tay ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u00f4ng v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam \u2018bom t\u1ea5n\u2019 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Riyad Mahrez t\u1eeb Leicester City.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Raheem Sterling \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00fap b\u1ea1c Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u1ee7a Man City \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp sau Arguero trong danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1456","checkdouble":"191666"},{"date":"15:28 20/07","title":"Mourinho nh\u1eafn Sanchez: \u201c\u0110\u1ebfn M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ra s\u00e2n!\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/22/mourinho-yeu-cau-sanchez-ra-san-den-my-va-lap-tuc-ra-san.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 khen ng\u1ee3i sao tr\u1ebb Tahith Chong sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa Man United v\u00e0 Club America h\u00f4m nay.</h2><h2>Tahith Chong ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Juan Mata. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-1 sau khi Man United b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTahith Chong l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 Herrera b\u0103ng v\u00e0o d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng d\u1ed9i c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Mata s\u00fat b\u1ed3i tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Club America.</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Chong\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Tahith Chong sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Club America h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Tahith Chong sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Club America h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/mourinho-khen-ngoi-dac-biet-sao-tre-tahith-chong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Tahith Chong sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Club America</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-club-america-tran-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191627.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Club America vs MU</span>, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Man United, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 18 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTahith Chong ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. V\u00e0 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cQu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Mata l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n m\u00e0 Chong \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin khi ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cD\u1eabu v\u1eady, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng khi v\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n c\u00f3. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t\".</em></div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMourinho l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cho sao tr\u1ebb ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Mourinho c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng Chong c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t Man United \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. B\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i \u1edf h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng. K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t c\u00f2n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 mong manh v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1455","checkdouble":"191669"},{"date":"15:15 20/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 0-0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (H2): C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/can-tho-vs-sai-gon-vong-20-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 20/7.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018 l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 20/7.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/can-tho-vs-sai-gon-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191671.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP C\u1ea6N TH\u01a0 VS S\u00c0I G\u00d2N</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1454","checkdouble":"191671"},{"date":"16:04 20/07","title":"Sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh NHA b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/zaha-muon-roi-crystal-palace-va-tin-vui-cho-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tin vui cho m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t CLB \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh nh\u01b0 Everton, Tottenham hay Borussia Dortmund.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Zaha \u0111\u1eaft h\u00e0ng tr\u00ean TTCN</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWilfried Zaha tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace. Anh g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man United mua v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2013 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV David Moyes, Zaha kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u. Anh b\u1ecb \u0111em cho Cardiff m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf n\u1eeda sau m\u00f9a 2013/14. Ngay sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em b\u00e1n l\u1ea1i cho CLB c\u0169 Crystal Palace.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/15/Zaha-muon-roi-Crystal-Palace-va-tu-choi-gia-han-hop-dong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd t\u1edbi Wilfried Zaha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n4 n\u0103m tr\u00f4i qua, Zaha v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh gi\u00fap Palace \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Zaha l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i l\u1edbn h\u01a1n Palace. Nh\u1eefng Everton, Tottenham hay Borussia Dortmund \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u0169i c\u00f4ng s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace v\u00e0 m\u1edbi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB n\u00e0y. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Palace \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb Zaha k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 125 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng anh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Wilfried Zaha\" title=\"tien ve Wilfried Zaha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/zaha-muon-roi-crystal-palace-va-tin-vui-cho-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Zaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nZaha cho hay quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean quan nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng. C\u1ed1t l\u00f5i l\u00e0 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u tham v\u1ecdng h\u01a1n. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i g\u1ea7n 26, Zaha tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed s\u1ee9c \u1edf CLB l\u1edbn m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Zaha v\u1edbi Palace c\u00f2n t\u1edbi 4 n\u0103m v\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i. Nghe \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Selhurst Park y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng NHA tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-chia-tay-sterling-172-191666.html\">Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ly-do-liverpool-danh-bai-chelsea-vu-alisson-172-191664.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1ee5 Alisson</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lucas-digne-chuan-bi-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191654.html\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-courois-172-191653.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ed1t 3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay th\u1ebf Courtois</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1453","checkdouble":"191673"}]}